steps.name: I check that the "Welcome Screen" is displayed
I click on "GET STARTED" button
I check that the "Choose Data Preferences Screen" is displayed
I click on "ALLOW ALL TRACKING" button
I check that the "First SignIn Screen" is displayed
I click on "SIGN IN WITH EMAIL" button
I click on "EMAIL ADDRESS" input
I enter the email address "janusz.nowicki@xktzxit.mail" in the input
I click on "LET'S GO" button
I check that the "Password Screen" is displayed
I click on "PASSWORD" input
I enter the password "#Test123" in the input
I click on "SIGN IN" button
I check that the "Notification Permission Screen" is displayed
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I check that the "Location Permission Flow Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Location Permission Flow Screen" is displayed
I click on "CONTINUE" button
I accept the new terms and conditions
I accept Updated Terms and Conditions
I accept Terms & Conditions
I close "Tell Us What You Think Pane"
I skip linking my card
I handle"Stay Informed About Offers Pane" marketing consent
I dismiss "Stay Informed About Offers Pane" marketing consent
I click on "MAYBE LATER" button
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I click on "PROFILE" tab
I check that the "Profile Screen" is displayed
I get the text from the "MOBILE PHONE NUMBER" text
I check that the application text: "+48790590000" is equals to expected value: "+48790590000"
I get the text from the "EMAIL ADDRESS" input
I check that the application text: "janusz.nowicki@xktzxit.mail" is equals to expected value: "janusz.nowicki@xktzxit.mail"
I click on "DELETE MY ACCOUNT" button
I swipe on the device screen to the "DOWN"
I check that the "Delete Your Account Pane" is displayed
I click on "YES, DELETE MY ACCOUNT" button
I get the text from the "SIGN IN OR SIGN UP" button
I check that the application text: "SIGN IN OR SIGN UP" is equals to expected value: "SIGN IN OR SIGN UP"
I close and open application
I check that the "Welcome Screen" is displayed
I click on "GET STARTED" button
I check that the "Choose Data Preferences Screen" is displayed
I click on "ALLOW ALL TRACKING" button
I check that the "First SignIn Screen" is displayed
I click on "SIGN IN WITH EMAIL" button
I enter the email address "janusz.nowicki@xktzxit.mail" in the input
I click on "LET'S GO" button
I get the text from the top text area on the "Sign Up Screen"
I check that the application text: "Welcome back" is equals to expected value: "Create Account"
